        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asking Austin's intervention in behalf of Mrs. League.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Col. Stephen F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>Dear Sir my <persName>wife </persName>will start <date when="1830-11-12">tomorrow morning</date> to remove to
<placeName>Jennings Camp</placeName> it is unnecessary for me to attempt a description
of her deplorable situation and feelings, or my own I have not
sufficient use of my faculties to address you as I would wish, but
I call upon your humanity and merciful feelings to come down and
see and have an interview with<persName> Mrs League </persName>before she starts and
also with myself</p>

<p><persName>H H League</persName></p>

<p><date when="1830-11-13">Nov&#8212;13th&#8212;1830</date></p>


        </div1>
